  • Field Details

    • resolvedDerivationPath

      @NonNull public final Uri resolvedDerivationPath
      The resolved derivation path corresponding to this account public key. This is fully resolved to the canonical representation for the WalletContractV1.PURPOSE_* and key derivation scheme.

    • CREATOR

  • Constructor Details

    • PublicKeyResponse

      public PublicKeyResponse(@Nullable byte[] publicKey, @Nullable String publicKeyEncoded, @NonNull Uri resolvedDerivationPath)
      Construct a new PublicKeyResponse
      Parameters:
      publicKey - an account public key. If publicKey is null, this indicates that this response is for an account which does not exist in the account derivation scheme.
      publicKeyEncoded - the encoded account public key. The encoding scheme depends on the authorized purpose of the seed from which this account is derived (for e.g. Base58 for WalletContractV1.PURPOSE_SIGN_SOLANA_TRANSACTION). If publicKey is null, this should also be null. If publicKey is non-null, this should be the encoded representation of publicKey (or an empty string, if no encoding is specified for this WalletContractV1.PURPOSE_*.
      resolvedDerivationPath - the fully resolved derivation path for this account public key
